d cause the  device not to meet the published specifications.    DISCLAIMER  SG Micro Corp reserves the right to make any change in  circuit design, or specifications without prior notice.             High-Accuracy Supervisory Circuit  SGM820xQ  with Integrated Watchdog Timer      5  DECEMBER 2023  SG Micro Corp  www.sg-micro.com  "}'
